                             java.util.Set<Fact> provFacts)

Generates a new set of hypotheses, when invoked by the library.

Parameters:
provEvents - The subset of the requested events (the events requested using the generateHypotheses method) which are available at the leaf for which hypotheses are being generated.
provFacts - The subset of the requested facts (the facts requested using the generateHypotheses method) which are available at the leaf for which hypotheses are being generated.
